{"word":"μινύρομαι","slug":"μινύρομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μινύρομαι</b></el> <el>(μῐνύρομαι,) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, = <a href='S:μινυρίζω'><el>μινυρίζω</el></a>, of the nightingale, <i>to warble</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>: <i>to hum a tune</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}